---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Ask Me Anything">
    <section id="register">
        <div class="flex-container">
            <div class="left">
                <h5 class="exam">Join Us For</h5>
                <h2>
                    Ask Me Anything
                </h2>
                <p class="description">
                    Join our weekly "Ask Me Anything" session, a dedicated space designed for anyone curious or working within the tech world. Whether you're pondering the best path to land a specific tech job, trying to understand different system architectures, stuck on a tricky coding problem, or just have general questions about the industry, this is your chance to get direct answers and insights. It's an open forum where you can bring your queries, big or small, and receive personalized guidance, making it a valuable opportunity to learn, clarify doubts, and connect with others interested in technology.
                </p>
                <h4>Timing</h4>
                <p>Every Wednesday: 5pm - 6pm (AEST) on Zoom.</p>
                <h4>Additional Details</h4>
                <p>Limited to 10 seats per session. You may register for as many sessions as you'd like but be courteous to others. If you don't believe you can make it then please cancel.</p>
